data.description: Great Townhome located in the desirable Regal Palms Resort! Townhome is located on Verona Ave. Close to the Clubhouse and Pool. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a vacation home in the resort community of Regal Palms. This fully furnished townhome is turnkey and ready to be called home as a vacation/short term rental or primary residence! This home is close to the amenities, which is extremely important for a successful short term rental property in Regal Palms. This 4 bedroom 3 bathroom townhouse features an open first floor layout. Full master bedroom with an optional lockout entrance/exit on the first floor with on-suite bathroom, Jack and Jill style opening to the bedroom and foyer. Three additional spacious bedrooms upstairs and two full baths. The master bedroom includes an on-suite bathroom with garden tub and nice closet with optional owner’s closet lockout. Updates include: kitchen renovation; appliances; furniture; full interior paint. Regal Palms is ~15-20 minutes to Disney property with astounding amenities: TWO pools, one with a slide, lazy river & zero point entry. Poolside tiki bar, sand volleyball, onsite reception, indoor & outdoor spa, fitness center, sauna/steam room, ice cream shop, game room & NEWLY remodeled on-site restaurant. This gated community has so much to offer and walking distance to grocery store (Publix), many restaurants, ice cream shop, bank, pharmacy, emergency clinic and much more! All sizes are approximate, please measure for accuracy. All room, home & lot size are estimated, exact measurements and HOA fees.
